  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate the efficacy of the Kreiger/Kunz method of Therapeutic Touch on
      function, pain perception and quality of life in persons with Osteoarthritis in the knee.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
